Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.util

Interface Stack<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - Type of data to be stored in the Stack
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArrayStack, LinkedStack
    public interface Stack<E>
    Abstract interface for Stack type collections, in which elements can only be accessed if they are "on top." Also includes field related methods as well as accessors.
    Author:
    Hunter Pruitt
